On our last renovation we committed to a solution that would help us immensely reduce plastic waste. 
Together with the people at @moma_melkboer we implemented a reusable bucket milk system that reduces milk related plastic waste to 0.

At the same time, this type of tap system minimises milk waste due to human error, helps in the consistency of our work and it is an ergonomic solution to a very repetitive task in our workflow!
